T1  - Who pays for bank insolvency in transition and emerging economies?
AU  - Mayes, David G.
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 29
IS  - 1
SP  - 161
EP  - 181
PY  - 2005
DA  - 2005/01/01/
T2  - Banking and the Financial Sector in Transition and Emerging Market Economies
SN  - 0378-4266
